author: Lauren Egan
title: Trump encourages anti-lockdown group opposed to stay-at-home order in Minnesota
description: President Donald Trump threw his support behind several anti-lockdown groups Friday that are holding protests around the country against state stay-at-home orders that health experts say are needed to stop the spread of the coronavirus and save lives.
content:
WASHINGTON President Donald Trump on Friday encouraged an anti-lockdown group that is scheduled to protest in Minnesota against stay-at-home orders to prevent the spread of coronavirus and he appeared to back such efforts in other states.
